data.description: NO BOND! Roof replaced in 2015.  Don't miss out on this 2 bedroom, 2 bath, 2 car garage villa in The Village of Santo Domingo.  The kitchen is extended, all floors are Tile or Vinyl, NO CAPRET.  The relaxing Florida Room is to die for, it gives you an escape into your own peaceful area for reading, coffee or relaxing watching tv.  A nice and cozy room that you will love.  An inside laundry room which gives you extra room in the garage for storage.  Newer stainless steel appliances.  There is also a closet pantry plus plenty of room for a table and chairs.  Both bathroom are spacious.  Low maintenance in the yard.  Location, Location, Location.... Near Spanish Springs, Savannah Center, restaurants and hospitals are close by.  Schedule a tour today!
